---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Delivery Information | fashionCulture">
    <main>
        <section class="delivery-info-section">
            <h1>Delivery Information</h1>

            <div class="content-block">
                <p>
                    At fashionCulture, we strive to ensure that your order reaches you as quickly and efficiently as possible. Below, you'll find important information regarding our delivery processes, options, and policies.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Shipping Destinations</h2>
                <p>
                    We are pleased to offer shipping to a wide range of international destinations. During the checkout process, you will be able to select your country from the dropdown list to see if we ship to your location.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Please note that certain remote locations may have limited shipping options, and additional fees may apply.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Shipping Methods & Costs</h2>
                <p>
                    We offer a variety of shipping methods to meet your needs. Shipping costs and delivery times will vary depending on your location and the shipping method selected during checkout. Available shipping methods include:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Standard Shipping:</strong> Estimated delivery within 5-7 business days.</li>
                    <li><strong>Express Shipping:</strong> Estimated delivery within 2-3 business days.</li>
                    <li><strong>Next-Day Shipping:</strong> Next-day delivery for orders placed before 12:00 PM.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    Shipping costs are calculated at checkout based on the weight of your order and your delivery location.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Order Processing Time</h2>
                <p>
                    All orders are processed within 1-2 business days. Orders are not processed or shipped on weekends or holidays. If we are experiencing a high volume of orders, processing times may be delayed. In such cases, we will notify you via email.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Order Tracking</h2>
                <p>
                    Once your order has been shipped, you will receive a shipping confirmation email that includes a tracking number. You can use this tracking number to monitor the status of your delivery through the carrierâ€™s website.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Customs, Duties, and Taxes</h2>
                <p>
                    fashionCulture is not responsible for any customs fees, duties, or taxes that may be applied to your order. All fees imposed during or after shipping are the responsibility of the customer (tariffs, taxes, etc.).
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Delivery Issues</h2>
                <p>
                    If you encounter any issues with your delivery, such as a delayed, lost, or damaged package, please contact our customer support team at <a href="mailto:support@fashionCulture.com">support@fashionCulture.com</a>. We will work with you and the carrier to resolve the issue as quickly as possible.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Changes to Delivery Information</h2>
                <p>
                    fashionCulture reserves the right to update or modify this delivery information at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting to the website. We encourage you to review this page periodically to stay informed of any updates.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <style>
          main {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 100px auto 0;
        }

        .delivery-info-section {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #444;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #555;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .content-block {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        strong {
            color: #000;
        }

        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</Layout>
